                  <rs id="t18800112-146-offence-1" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18800112-146-offence-1" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18800112-146-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>, Stealing a stockand two center<lb></lb>bits of <persName id="t18800112-name-38" type="victimName">
